						               													<description>The hilarious party game of made up acronyms that will have you LOL with your BFFs!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Over six rounds collect points ( and try not to lose any).  While thinking of the funniest acronyms from the letters and subject.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;One person draws three cards each with a letter on it, then they draw a category card.  Flip the timer and go, think up the best acronyms that fit the category and the three letters.  Once time runs out take turns reading what you feel is your best answer.  Each person votes who they think gave the best acronym and every vote counts as a point.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During speed rounds, who ever is in the lead starts.  They must think of the first acronym on the fly and say it outloud then play passes to the next player.  When the timer stops, that player loses two points.  After six rounds tally up the points, and the most wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
